name: JAPANESE RAMEN KIT
description: “Say hello to an irresistible ramen, made easy. Just like my authentic dumplings range in the freezer, my signature Japanese Ramen recipe takes traditional Asian flavours and makes them effortless to enjoy at home. With my rich shoyu broth and soft, silky noodles ready to go, all that’s left to do is add meat, veggies and classic hard boiled eggs for a ramen worth raving about. Thanks for inviting me to dinner at your house”.
